Release Information

The most feature-packed media server available
today. Stream movies, TV shows, music, photos and
subtitles to all the UPnP and DLNA-enabled devices
in your home - TVs, Blu-ray players, PS3, Xbox 360
home theater and media players. On-the-fly
transcoding. Multiple device support. Powerful
organizing features. Extensive media format
support
